{"tid":2263642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約前沙展參與「獵狐行動」 被控任中國政府代理人","createTime":"2020-10-30T04:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T06:26:17.000Z","uid":364767,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba877c315942f38b7d5caf245710ef5c199c6dfc","tid":2263642,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦調查局（FBI）日前起訴8人，指控他們在美國境內參與中國的「獵狐行動」，脅迫在美中國公民回中國受審。《紐約郵報》報道，8名被告中，包括一名53歲私家偵探麥馬漢（Michael McMahon），是紐約巿警察局（NYPD）前沙展。他被控在美國非法擔任外國政府代理人，以50萬美元保釋，一旦定罪最高可判入獄五年。<br />\n<br />\n53歲的麥馬漢曾任職紐約巿警察局警員14年，職位至沙展，隸屬布朗克斯（The Bronx）43警區；後因執勤造成不明傷殘，提早退休，一直領取警員長俸。其妻子為女演員拜恩（Martha Byrne），1985年至2009年曾參演哥倫比亞電視台（CBS）肥皂劇《As the World Turns》。<br />\n<br />\n麥馬漢離開警隊後，在2003年6月自組偵探社「麥馬漢調查集團」（McMahon Investigative Group），在新澤西州領有偵探牌照執業。他周三被起訴參與中國「獵狐行動」，被指騷擾、監視和恐嚇一名在新澤西州居住的前中國官員，脅迫他回中國受審。<br />\n<br />\n法庭文件指，麥馬漢2016年6月受僱於中國，開始調查和監視該名中國官員，其後參與一連串威嚇行動，包括展開跟蹤；把受害人在中國的年老父親帶到美國，威迫受害人回中國；在受害人家門外貼恐嚇字條，要求受害人回中國服刑10年，以換取妻兒平安；把私家車長期停泊在受害人家外等。但這些行動都無法迫使受害人回中國。<br />\n<br />\n文件指，案中另一名被告、紐約巿皇后區居民朱峰（音譯，Zhu Feng），在2017年4月11日曾傳短訊給麥馬漢，分享自己過去停泊汽車作出恐嚇的經驗。<br />\n<br />\n朱峰發出上述短訊翌日，他經新澤西州紐瓦克機場（Newark Airport）離境，前往中國，被當局在行李搜出夜視鏡等裝備。之後他傳短訊給同黨，促請他們刪除通訊記錄。最終，麥馬漢與另外四名中國人同黨，於美國被補；朱峰和另外兩名同黨則成功逃走，相信已返回中國。<br />\n<br />\nurl]<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201030/OHB2CW33KVAJPNEIBWUBPGTKFU/[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201030%2FOHB2CW33KVAJPNEIBWUBPGTKFU%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=363e7106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201030%2FOHB2CW33KVAJPNEIBWUBPGTKFU%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&h=7fb9808d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201030/OHB2CW33KVAJPNEIBWUBPGTKFU/[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n可想而知 中共勢力在美國 滲透得有多厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4623020a11292c36e66dc601b14d3044215a2ca","tid":2263642,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"搵食啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3191e813566d7587ba882e69709dc49218cd34bd","tid":2263642,"uid":222970,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"究竟NYPD有幾多鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200922/CZODNZ7S5BDCRGCUQGBL7VZSSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200922%2FCZODNZ7S5BDCRGCUQGBL7VZSSM%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=a77e1d07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200922%2FCZODNZ7S5BDCRGCUQGBL7VZSSM%2F&h=10647940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200922/CZODNZ7S5BDCRGCUQGBL7VZSSM/</a>"},{"pid":"850abbf5a7f99dffa07019f9fc9172f7454b9c52","tid":2263642,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00a4552d312ea26481bc5aadf46e95220e0f6ef","tid":2263642,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"支共全民間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e5e383eb94c4a75043f26b93727b709d80aef6","tid":2263642,"uid":377617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:21:44.000Z","msg":"宜家中共用滲透控制成個地球咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25344cd2edb3a606c33a31c3f391abe455c73383","tid":2263642,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"根本要拘捕哂所有華人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ee2846193fbff74dcd81635ac51f8ddfdd3b0d","tid":226